OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers clearing eastern parts, then
OL,7,Fsunny spells for many this evening. A
OL,8,Fdry night follows with clear spells,
OL,9,Fbut showers or rain into western parts
OL,10,Fby dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with early rain
OL,13,Ffollowed by sunny spells and blustery
OL,14,Fshowers on Tuesday, with a risk of
OL,15,Fhail and thunder. Feeling cool for the
OL,16,Ftime of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
